      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SNACK DRAGON (3) is a progressive type who recorded his 2nd career win last time out (19.91) at this track. Hard to go past form here at this journey. Great chance to get the job done again. BLUE ART (6) goes very well this course and distance starting 33 times for 12 wins and 16 minors. Hit the frame latest (27.92) when third at Casino in a NG. Can feature in the finish. BOOM TOWN (1) has some solid form under his belt and proved too strong last time to win by 0.8 lengths at Q Lakeside in a handy 21.84 beating Magic Shazam. Form is hard to fault from this box, with a win and two minor placings from three starts. Can continue on with his winning form. JANE'S JET (2) was well fancied in betting last start but could only manage a neck away in second (21.91). Some good form is emerging from his last run.",
